10. Saḷavagga 
97. Pamādavihārīsutta 
“Pamādavihāriñca vo, bhikkhave, desessāmi appamādavihāriñca. 
Taṃ suṇātha. 
Kathañca, bhikkhave, pamādavihārī hoti? 
Cakkhundriyaṃ asaṃvutassa, bhikkhave, viharato cittaṃ byāsiñcati cakkhuviññeyyesu rūpesu. 
